===Noun===
'''withers''' 
# The part of the [[back]] of a [[draft]] [[animal]] or [[horse]] that is the [[highest]], between the [[shoulder blades]]

====Usage notes====
Although this noun refers to one object, there is no corresponding singular form for this word.

